items.title: Videogame soundtracks Wiki
items.headline: Find new things at the Vgost Wikia
items.desc: Have you ever been playing a game and wondered about the game's soundtrack? If so the Vgost Wikia or the Video Game Soundtracks Wikia community is the place for you. At the Vghost Wikia, we attempt to document and make articles about video game soundtracks. Please feel free to join us in helping make this a greater source for video game soundtracks.
